id: pm-aw7d
title: SDK lacks assertRegisteredCommandOverride testing helper (coverage gap in testing.ts)
description: "src/sdk/testing.ts exports assertRegisteredCommandContract (for registerCommand definitions), assertRegisteredHook, assertRegisteredSearchProvider, assertRegisteredVectorStoreAdapter, assertRegisteredImporter, assertRegisteredExporter, assertRegisteredItemField, assertRegisteredItemType, assertPackageManifest. It does NOT export assertRegisteredCommandOverride, assertRegisteredParserOverride, assertRegisteredPreflightOverride, or assertRegisteredRendererOverride. Extensions using registerCommand(command, override), registerParser, registerPreflight, or registerRenderer have no SDK assertion helper to verify their override registered correctly. This forces package authors to directly inspect the ExtensionCommandRegistry internals."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 3
tags[4]: "area:extensions","area:sdk",dx,testing
